## Product defaults (do not reopen without ask)

- **Primary surface:** always-on secondary monitor (Innie-Cam desk ambient)
- **Phone:** first-class habit logger (portal + thumb UI) — equal polish planned, monitor ships first
- **Ambient:** rare (45m+ cooldown, 0–2/session); tiers A cosmetic / B micro-reward / C gameplay
- **Habit core:** engine v2 protocol-bin snapshot (`engine.js`); same five protocols/targets; extend via ambient + copy, don’t add parallel math in `app.js`
- **Stack:** stay vanilla ES modules

## Voice

Clinical Lumon handbook. Prefer refinement / compliance / Board / workstation / file / temper. Avoid generic habit-tracker or purple cyber aesthetics.
